# ===== EASIEST SETUP: Travelpayouts only (personal email, instant token) =====
# 1. Sign up free: https://www.travelpayouts.com  (no business verification)
# 2. Dashboard -> Tools -> API: copy your Token and Marker
TP_TOKEN=paste_your_token_here
TP_MARKER=paste_your_marker_here

# ===== OPTIONAL extra provider: Duffel (live airline offers) =====
# Skip this if the signup feels heavy - the app works fully without it.
DUFFEL_API_KEY=
